@baseUrl = http://localhost:6013
@adminKey = change-me
@sessionId = 11111111-1111-1111-1111-111111111111

### Sync products into pgvector store
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/ai/admin/sync/products
X-Nexus-AI-Key: {{adminKey}}

### Search synced products
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/ai/admin/search?query=wireless%20headphones&topK=5
X-Nexus-AI-Key: {{adminKey}}

### Start or continue a grounded chat session
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/ai/chat/sessions
Content-Type: application/json

{
	"sessionId": "{{sessionId}}",
	"userId": "demo-user",
	"message": "Recommend a good budget gaming mouse and explain why.",
	"topK": 5
}

### Read chat history
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/ai/chat/sessions/{{sessionId}}
